# ============================================================================
# IMPORTANT: Netlify Environment Variables Setup
# ============================================================================
# ALL 5 variables below MUST be set in Netlify for ALL deploy contexts:
# 1. Go to: Netlify Dashboard → Site Settings → Environment Variables
# 2. Add EACH variable below (both NEXT_PUBLIC_* and VITE_* prefixes) for:
#    - Production deploys (main branch)
#    - Deploy Previews (PR deploys)  
#    - Branch deploys (all branches)
# 3. DO NOT mark as "Secret" - these are public client keys
# 4. After setting, trigger "Clear cache and deploy" to ensure fresh build
#
# Variables to set in Netlify:
#   - NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL
#   - NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
#   - NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL (use production URL: https://xdrivelogistics.co.uk)
#   - VITE_SUPABASE_URL
#   - VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
#
# For detailed setup instructions, see: NETLIFY_SETUP.md
# For complete documentation, see: ENVIRONMENT_VARIABLES.md
# For Romanian guide, see: CONFIGURARE_CHEI_SUPABASE.md
